---
import SectionHeader from "../ui/SectionHeader.astro";
---

<section class="border-b border-white/5">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 py-24 sm:py-32">
    <SectionHeader eyebrow="Technical paper" align="left" maxW="max-w-5xl" mb="mb-10">
      A product-grade paper for <span class="text-amber-300">agent-undo</span>,
      not hand-wavy launch fluff.
    </SectionHeader>

    <div class="grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[1.1fr_0.9fr]">
      <div data-reveal class="rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] p-7">
        <p class="max-w-3xl text-[16px] leading-8 text-white/65">
          The paper frames agent-undo as a local provenance-and-rollback substrate for agent-written
          code, then backs it with a real artifact snapshot, two workload measurements, and explicit
          limits on what is still unmeasured.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          <a
            href="/paper"
            class="inline-flex h-11 items-center rounded-md bg-amber-400 px-5 text-sm font-semibold text-black transition-colors hover:bg-amber-300"
          >
            Read the paper page
          </a>
          <a
            href="/papers/agent-undo-paper.pdf"
            class="inline-flex h-11 items-center rounded-md border border-white/15 px-5 text-sm font-medium text-white transition-colors hover:border-white/35 hover:bg-white/[0.05]"
          >
            Download PDF
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8 grid gap-3 sm:grid-cols-3">
          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] p-4">
            <div class="text-[11px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-white/40">binary</div>
            <div class="mt-2 text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight text-white">4.85 MiB</div>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] p-4">
            <div class="text-[11px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-white/40">write detect</div>
            <div class="mt-2 text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight text-white">157–161 ms</div>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] p-4">
            <div class="text-[11px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-white/40">oops</div>
            <div class="mt-2 text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight text-white">7–8 ms</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div data-reveal class="overflow-hidden rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-black/20 p-3">
        <img
          src="/papers/agent-undo-microeval.svg"
          alt="agent-undo micro-evaluation chart comparing synthetic and repo-snapshot workloads"
          class="block w-full"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
